{
  "title": "ISic002946. Dedication to Artemis",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Επὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δινυσίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δινυσίου\">Δινυσίου</span></span> ἱ[ερέως] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φιλοκράτης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φιλοκράτης\">Φιλοκράτης</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ξένων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ξένων\">Ξ[ένων?]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμιτι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμιτι\">Ἀρτέμιτι</span></span> εὐ[χην] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΕΠΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δινυσίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δινυσίου\">ΔΙΝΥΣΙΟΥ</span></span>Ι[.....]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φιλοκράτης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φιλοκράτης\">ΦΙΛΟΚΡΑΤΗΣ</span></span>ΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ξένων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ξένων\">Ξ[....]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμιτι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρτέμιτι\">ΑΡΤΕΜΙΤΙ</span></span>ΕΥ[...]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002946_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002946_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002946.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic002946-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro 1965</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>In the priesthood of Dionysios. Philokrates and Xenon(?), (made) a vow to Artemis</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Classified as a fake by Kaibel, without autopsy, both Orsi and Manganaro's autopsy confirms the text as genuine</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li>  <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\"> 14.0012*</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Orsi 1900 55 no. 27 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001707\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001707</a></li><li> Soraci 1958 253 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001571\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001571</a></li><li> Manganaro 1963 57 n.42 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850</a></li><li> Manganaro 1965 176 fig.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001452\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001452</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Large, wide, simple letters, alpha with straight bar, omicron circular and very slightly smaller than other letters and mid-line.</p> Line 1-3  40-50  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
